				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2008/08/bush-evangelizing-in-china-during-the-olympics/" title="Permalink to Bush Evangelizing in China during the Olympics?!" rel="bookmark">Bush Evangelizing in China during the Olympics?!</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2008-08-11T00:19:56+0000">Monday, August 11th, 2008</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
